{{Infobox television | show_name = Azhdar Show | genre = [[Variety Show]] | starring = [[Azhdar Wahbi]] | country = [[Kurdistan]] | language = | num_seasons = <!-- or num_series --> | num_episodes = | executive_producer = | producer = | location = | runtime = | company = | distributor = | channel = [[Korek TV]] | picture_format = | first_run = | first_aired = October 2009 | last_aired = | website = [https://web.archive.org/web/20091126003939/http://www.korek.tv:80/ Azhdar Show] }}
The '''Azhdar Show''' is a live [[Kurdish people|Kurdish]] variety program hosted by the pop star, singer and entertainer [[Azhdar Wahbi]] in [[Kurdistan]]. The show features interviews and performances by Azhdar and his guests. The show has been on the air since October 2009 and airs every Friday night on [[Korek TV]].
